{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775886158454,"sessionID":"ses_284f48b9fffeAzMtlRGIfh6tQM","part":{"id":"prt_d7b100303001ggqbVLZKU3RqXd","messageID":"msg_d7b0f15d8001m6Gv1l0Qz0HC5k","sessionID":"ses_284f48b9fffeAzMtlRGIfh6tQM","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_e843124393b549729f7a5be8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Privacy Policy - AgentCube Dify Plugin\n\n## Last Updated: April 11, 2026\n\n## Introduction\n\nThis Privacy Policy describes how AgentCube handles data when processing code execution requests through the Dify plugin integration.\n\n## Data Collection\n\n### Information We Process\n\nWhen you use the AgentCube plugin, the following data is processed:\n\n1. **Code Content**: The source code or commands submitted for execution\n2. **Execution Results**: Output, errors, and exit codes from code execution\n3. **Session Metadata**: Session IDs, timestamps, and execution duration\n4. **File Content**: Files uploaded to or downloaded from the sandbox environment\n\n### Information We Do NOT Collect\n\n- Personal identifying information\n- API credentials or authentication tokens\n- User account information from Dify\n\n## Data Usage\n\nThe data processed by AgentCube is used solely for:\n\n1. **Code Execution**: Running the submitted code in a sandboxed environment\n2. **Result Generation**: Capturing and returning execution output\n3. **Session Management**: Maintaining execution state when session reuse is enabled\n4. **Service Improvement**: Aggregated, anonymized metrics for service optimization\n\n## Data Storage\n\n### Temporary Storage\n\n- Code and files are stored temporarily in Kubernetes ephemeral storage\n- Session data persists only for the duration of the session\n- All temporary data is deleted when sessions are terminated\n\n### No Long-term Storage\n\nAgentCube does not permanently store:\n- Executed code\n- Execution results\n- Uploaded or downloaded files\n- Session information\n\n## Data Sharing\n\nAgentCube does not share, sell, or transfer your data to third parties except:\n\n1. **Service Providers**: Kubernetes infrastructure providers hosting the sandbox\n2. **Legal Requirements**: When required by law or to protect rights and safety\n\n## Security Measures\n\nWe implement the following security measures:\n\n1. **Sandbox Isolation**: Each execution runs in an isolated Kubernetes pod\n2. **Network Policies**: Restricted network access for sandbox environments\n3. **Resource Limits**: CPU and memory quotas prevent resource exhaustion\n4. **Ephemeral Storage**: All data is stored in temporary, non-persistent volumes\n\n## Data Retention\n\n- **Active Sessions**: Data retained for the duration of the session\n- **Completed Sessions**: Data deleted immediately after session termination\n- **Logs**: Operational logs retained for up to 30 days for debugging purposes\n\n## User Rights\n\nUsers have the right to:\n\n1. **Access**: Request information about data processed\n2. **Deletion**: Request immediate session termination and data deletion\n3. **Portability**: Export execution history from Dify platform\n\n## Compliance\n\nAgentCube is designed to support compliance with:\n\n- GDPR (General Data Protection Regulation)\n- CCPA (California Consumer Privacy Act)\n- SOC 2 Type II security standards\n\n## Children's Privacy\n\nAgentCube is not intended for users under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect data from children.\n\n## Changes to This Policy\n\nWe may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Changes will be:\n\n- Documented in the plugin repository\n- Effective immediately upon publication\n- Communicated through the Dify platform when significant\n\n## Contact Information\n\nFor privacy-related questions:\n\n- **GitHub**: https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n- **Issues**: https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/issues\n- **Email**: privacy@agentcube.dev (if applicable)\n\n## Acknowledgments\n\nThis privacy policy is designed for open-source software and may be adapted for similar projects.\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/integrations/dify-plugin/PRIVACY.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/integrations/dify-plugin/main.py\">\nERROR [3:6] Import \"dify_plugin\" could not be resolved\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.py\">\nERROR [5:6] Import \"dify_plugin\" could not be resolved\nERROR [6:6] Import \"dify_plugin.errors.tool\" could not be resolved\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py\">\nERROR [6:6] Import \"dify_plugin\" could not be resolved\nERROR [7:6] Import \"dify_plugin.entities.tool\" could not be resolved\nERROR [8:6] Import \"agentcube\" could not be resolved\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/integrations/dify-plugin/tools/__init__.py\">\nERROR [3:6] Import \".agentcube_code_interpreter\" could not be resolved\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml\">\nERROR [74:14] Nested mappings are not allowed in compact mappings\nERROR [77:14] Nested mappings are not allowed in compact mappings\nERROR [134:14] Nested mappings are not allowed in compact mappings\nERROR [137:14] Nested mappings are not allowed in compact mappings\n</diagnostics>","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sdk-python/agentcube/__init__.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sdk-python/agentcube/code_interpreter.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/integrations/dify-plugin/main.py":[{"range":{"start":{"line":2,"character":5},"end":{"line":2,"character":16}},"message":"Import \"dify_plugin\" could not be resolved","severity":1,"code":"reportMissingImports","source":"Pyright","codeDescription":{"href":"https://github.com/microsoft/pyright/blob/main/docs/configuration.md#reportMissingImports"}}],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.py":[{"range":{"start":{"line":4,"character":5},"end":{"line":4,"character":16}},"message":"Import \"dify_plugin\" could not be resolved","severity":1,"code":"reportMissingImports","source":"Pyright","codeDescription":{"href":"https://github.com/microsoft/pyright/blob/main/docs/configuration.md#reportMissingImports"}},{"range":{"start":{"line":5,"character":5},"end":{"line":5,"character":28}},"message":"Import \"dify_plugin.errors.tool\" could not be resolved","severity":1,"code":"reportMissingImports","source":"Pyright","codeDescription":{"href":"https://github.com/microsoft/pyright/blob/main/docs/configuration.md#reportMissingImports"}}],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py":[{"range":{"start":{"line":5,"character":5},"end":{"line":5,"character":16}},"message":"Import \"dify_plugin\" could not be resolved","severity":1,"code":"reportMissingImports","source":"Pyright","codeDescri