{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775886379726,"sessionID":"ses_284f48b9fffeAzMtlRGIfh6tQM","part":{"id":"prt_d7b132c38001UY9rBNduSkgfeC","messageID":"msg_d7b1320a2001CxhCRKMAo5aP9q","sessionID":"ses_284f48b9fffeAzMtlRGIfh6tQM","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_cdffcaba13cb4ddf9e311108","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"identity:\n  name: agentcube-code-interpreter\n  author: agentcube\n  label:\n    human:\n      en_US: AgentCube Code Interpreter\n      ja_JP: AgentCube コードインタープリター\n      zh_Hans: AgentCube 代码解释器\n      pt_BR: Interpretador de Código AgentCube\n    llm:\n      en_US: Code execution tool for Python, JavaScript, and TypeScript in Kubernetes sandboxes\n      ja_JP: Kubernetes サンドボックスでの Python、JavaScript、TypeScript のコード実行ツール\n      zh_Hans: 在 Kubernetes 沙箱中执行 Python、JavaScript 和 TypeScript 代码的工具\n      pt_BR: Ferramenta de execução de código Python, JavaScript e TypeScript em sandboxes Kubernetes\n  description:\n    human:\n      en_US: Execute code and commands in secure sandboxed environments with file upload/download capabilities\n      ja_JP: ファイルのアップロード/ダウンロード機能を備えた安全なサンドボックス環境でコードやコマンドを実行\n      zh_Hans: 在具有文件上传/下载功能的安全沙箱环境中执行代码和命令\n      pt_BR: Execute código e comandos em ambientes sandbox seguros com recursos de upload/download de arquivos\n    llm:\n      en_US: Use this tool to execute Python, JavaScript, or TypeScript code in isolated Kubernetes sandbox environments. Supports code execution, command execution, file operations, and session management.\n      ja_JP: このツールを使用して、分離された Kubernetes サンドボックス環境で Python、JavaScript、TypeScript のコードを実行します。コード実行、コマンド実行、ファイル操作、セッション管理をサポートします。\n      zh_Hans: 使用此工具在隔离的 Kubernetes 沙箱环境中执行 Python、JavaScript 或 TypeScript 代码。支持代码执行、命令执行、文件操作和会话管理。\n      pt_BR: Use esta ferramenta para executar código Python, JavaScript ou TypeScript em ambientes sandbox Kubernetes isolados. Suporta execução de código, execução de comandos, operações de arquivo e gerenciamento de sessão.\nparameters:\n  - name: router_url\n    type: string\n    required: true\n    form: form\n    label:\n      en_US: Router URL\n      ja_JP: ルーター URL\n      zh_Hans: 路由器 URL\n      pt_BR: URL do Roteador\n    human_description:\n      en_US: Base URL of the AgentCube router service\n      ja_JP: AgentCube ルーターサービスのベース URL\n      zh_Hans: AgentCube 路由器服务的基础 URL\n      pt_BR: URL base do serviço do roteador AgentCube\n    llm_description: The base URL of the AgentCube router service for code execution requests\n  - name: workload_manager_url\n    type: string\n    required: true\n    form: form\n    label:\n      en_US: Workload Manager URL\n      ja_JP: ワークロードマネージャー URL\n      zh_Hans: 工作负载管理器 URL\n      pt_BR: URL do Gerenciador de Carga de Trabalho\n    human_description:\n      en_US: Base URL of the AgentCube workload manager service\n      ja_JP: AgentCube ワークロードマネージャーサービスのベース URL\n      zh_Hans: AgentCube 工作负载管理器服务的基础 URL\n      pt_BR: URL base do serviço do gerenciador de carga de trabalho AgentCube\n    llm_description: The base URL of the AgentCube workload manager service for session creation and management\n  - name: language\n    type: select\n    required: false\n    form: llm\n    options:\n      - value: python\n        label: python\n      - value: javascript\n        label: javascript\n      - value: typescript\n        label: typescript\n    label:\n      en_US: Programming Language\n      ja_JP: プログラミング言語\n      zh_Hans: 编程语言\n      pt_BR: Linguagem de Programação\n    human_description:\n      en_US: \"Programming language for code execution (default: python)\"\n      ja_JP: \"コード実行のプログラミング言語 (デフォルト：python)\"\n      zh_Hans: \"代码执行的编程语言 (默认：python)\"\n      pt_BR: \"Linguagem de programação para execução de código (padrão: python)\"\n    llm_description: The programming language to use for code execution. Choose from python, javascript, or typescript\n  - name: code\n    type: string\n    required: false\n    form: llm\n    label:\n      en_US: Code\n      ja_JP: コード\n      zh_Hans: 代码\n      pt_BR: Código\n    human_description:\n      en_US: Source code to execute in the sandbox\n      ja_JP: サンドボックスで実行するソースコード\n      zh_Hans: 在沙箱中执行的源代码\n      pt_BR: Código-fonte a ser executado na sandbox\n    llm_description: The source code to execute in the sandbox environment\n  - name: command\n    type: string\n    required: false\n    form: llm\n    label:\n      en_US: Command\n      ja_JP: コマンド\n      zh_Hans: 命令\n      pt_BR: Comando\n    human_description:\n      en_US: Shell command to execute in the sandbox\n      ja_JP: サンドボックスで実行するシェルコマンド\n      zh_Hans: 在沙箱中执行的 Shell 命令\n      pt_BR: Comando de shell a ser executado na sandbox\n    llm_description: A shell command to execute in the sandbox environment\n  - name: session_id\n    type: string\n    required: false\n    form: llm\n    label:\n      en_US: Session ID\n      ja_JP: セッション ID\n      zh_Hans: 会话 ID\n      pt_BR: ID da Sessão\n    human_description:\n      en_US: Existing session ID to reuse (optional)\n      ja_JP: 再利用する既存のセッション ID（オプション）\n      zh_Hans: 要重用的现有会话 ID（可选）\n      pt_BR: ID de sessão existente para reutilizar (opcional)\n    llm_description: An existing session ID to reuse for code execution, enabling stateful interactions\n  - name: session_reuse\n    type: boolean\n    required: false\n    form: llm\n    label:\n      en_US: Reuse Session\n      ja_JP: セッションを再利用\n      zh_Hans: 重用会话\n      pt_BR: Reutilizar Sessão\n    human_description:\n      en_US: \"Whether to reuse an existing session (default: false)\"\n      ja_JP: 既存のセッションを再利用するかどうか (デフォルト：false)\n      zh_Hans: 是否重用现有会话 (默认：false)\n      pt_BR: \"Se deve reutilizar uma sessão existente (padrão: false)\"\n    llm_description: Boolean flag indicating whether to reuse an existing session for stateful code execution\n  - name: code_interpreter_id\n    type: string\n    required: false\n    form: llm\n    label:\n      en_US: Code Interpreter ID\n      ja_JP: コードインタープリター ID\n      zh_Hans: 代码